     1	//! Unified API router for SafeClaw
     2	//!
     3	//! Merges all module routers into a single axum `Router` with CORS,
     4	//! consistent error handling, and a shared application state.
     5	//!
     6	//! ## Endpoint Map
     7	//!
     8	//! | Prefix                          | Module   | Description                    |
     9	//! |---------------------------------|----------|--------------------------------|
    10	//! | `/health`                       | runtime | Load balancer health probe     |
    11	//! | `/.well-known/a3s-service.json` | runtime | Service discovery              |
    12	//! | `/api/v1/gateway/*`             | runtime | Status, sessions, message, webhook |
    13	//! | `/api/v1/tee/status`            | runtime | TEE security level             |
    14	//! | `/api/v1/channels`              | runtime | Channel listing & config       |
    15	//! | `/api/v1/security/overview`     | runtime | Aggregated security dashboard  |
    16	//! | `/api/v1/taint/entries`         | runtime | Taint tracking entries         |
    17	//! | `/api/v1/memory/*`              | runtime | Memory layers, stats, export   |
    18	//! | `/api/v1/users`                 | runtime | User management (stub Phase 20)|
    19	//! | `/api/v1/privacy/*`             | privacy  | Classify, analyze, scan        |
    20	//! | `/api/v1/audit/*`               | leakage  | Audit events, stats, query     |
    21	//! | `/api/agent/*`                  | agent    | Agent sessions, backends       |
    22	//! | `/ws/agent/browser/:id`         | agent    | Agent WebSocket                |
